main event: Pilot visual with tail exhaust color gas seen to appear at 10° elevation and to disappear at 10° elevation at 310°.
interesting points: The object appeared to be very bright, round, and silver-colored.
The object was moving smoothly toward the east and blue-white in color.
The object disappeared suddenly as if a "flame out" at an approximate altitude of 3,000 feet.
The duration of sighting was approximately 1 minute.
witnesses: Capt. USAF, 17th Air Base Sq. "AL", Beach AFB, Florida
